anity metrics","Rotating account managers"],"afterItems":["Weekly reporting","Clear KPIs","Dedicated strategist","Revenue-focused metrics","Direct access to leadership"],"statusBefore":"Disconnected","statusAfter":"Revenue-aligned","dashboardBefore":"Q4 dashboard","dashboardAfter":"Live KPI board","pipelineLabel":"Pipeline value","pipelineBefore":"↓ 22%","pipelineAfter":"↑ 3.2×","statImpressions":"Impressions","statEngagement":"Engagement","statRevenue":"Revenue","beforeItemDetails":["Three-day email loops and vague updates. Urgent issues wait until your next scheduled call while ad spend keeps burning.","A PDF once a quarter, if you're lucky. No visibility into what's working, what's wasted, or what changed last week.","Black-box billing and unclear scope. You never know who's doing the work or where your budget actually goes.","They celebrate impressions and clicks while your pipeline stays flat. Activity looks busy. Revenue does not move.","Every quarter someone new owns your account. Context resets and you're re-explaining your business from scratch."],"afterItemDetails":["Every Monday: spend, leads, CPL, and pipeline in one digest. You always know where you stand and what's being optimized.","We agree on targets upfront: revenue, cost per lead, conversion rate. We report against them every week.","One senior strategist owns your account end-to-end. They know your business, market, and numbers. No handoffs.","We track what hits your P&L: qualified leads, close rate, ROAS, and LTV. Vanity metrics are context, never the headline.","Skip the ticket queue. When something matters, you're talking to decision-makers who can change direction fast."]},"cta":{"label":"Let's Talk","title":"Ready to Build a","titleHighlight":"Revenue System?","subtitle":"No rehearsed pitch. No pressure to sign anything.|Just a straightforward conversation about what real growth could look like for your business."},"midCta":{"label":"Next Step","title":"See what's possible|for your business","subtitle":"Book a strategy call or request a free audit.|We'll show you where your growth engine is leaking and how to fix it.","secondaryCta":"Get Free Audit"},"chatbot":{"openChat":"Open chat","closeChat":"Close chat","chatMessage":"Chat message","sendMessage":"Send message","assistantName":"KINEXIS AI","assistantRole":"Sales assistant","placeholder":"Type your answer...","initialMessage":"Quick question: are you looking for SEO, paid ads, web design, or something else?","questions":{"service":"What service are you looking for? (SEO, Paid Ads, Web Design, Funnels, Branding)","business":"What type of business do you run?","revenue":"What's your monthly revenue range?","goal":"What's your primary goal? (leads, sales, brand growth)"},"quickReplies":{"services":["SEO","Paid Ads","Web Design","Funnels","Branding"],"businessTypes":["E-Commerce","Local Service","SaaS","Professional Services"],"revenue":["Under $10k/mo","$$10k-$50k/mo","$$50k-$100k/mo","$$100k+/mo"],"goals":["More leads","More sales","Brand awareness","All of the above"]},"highIntentResponse":"You sound like a great fit! Let's get you booked for a strategy call. 👇","lowIntentResponse":"Thanks! Start with our free growth audit. It'll give you a clear picture of where to focus. 👇"},"cookies":{"title":"We use cookies","description":"We use essential cookies to run this site and, with your consent, analytics cookies to understand how visitors use kinexisdigital.com. See our","privacyLink":"Privacy Policy","accept":"Accept analytics","reject":"Reject non-essential"}},"now":"$undefined","timeZone":"America/Bogota","children":"$L18"}]
